      We are sending you this parental consent form to both inform you and to request permission for your child’s photo/image to potentially be posted on our website, as well as the company’s Facebook page and Instagram Account.

      As you are aware, there are potential dangers associated with the posting of personally identifiable information on a web site since global access to the Internet does not allow us to control who may access such information. These dangers have always existed; however, we as a Theater Company want to celebrate your child and his/her work. The law requires that we ask for your permission to use your child’s photo for public display.

      Pursuant to law, we will never release any personally identifiable information without prior written consent from you as parent or guardian. Personally identifiable information will only include student photo or video of performances.

      If you, as the parent or guardian, wish to rescind this agreement, you may do so at any time in writing by sending an email to actinglikeakidco@gmail.com


